observe ENERGY (Lyapunov) vs DISPLACEMENT (oscillation); flags = regime visited

  zeta     | E:osc conv div grew | x:osc conv div | reading
  -0.05	| E:Y - Y Y     | x:Y - Y      | DIVERGES (energy grew)
